  <widget type="label" version="2.0.0">
    <name>Label_8</name>
    <text>Knob value can be always visible, or displayed only when it differs from the readback one.

Knob value can be synced with the readback one, so that the knob will positioned at the read-back value.

When dragged, Knob can write the new target value on mouse button release, or continuously.

Extrema (maximum and minimum values) can be hidden.

Knob PV and readback PV can be different. Readback PV can be omitted.</text>
    <x>20</x>
    <y>510</y>
    <width>630</width>
    <height>180</height>
  </widget>
